ely.\n\nHere\u0027s the F# code to achieve this:\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060fsharp\nlet rec factorial n =\n    if n \u003C 0 then\n        \u0022Error: Negative input\u0022\n    elif n = 0 then\n        1\n    else\n        n * factorial (n - 1)\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\nThis function uses recursion to calculate the factorial of a number. It includes an edge case check for negative inputs, returning an error message if the input is negative.\n\n### Inform\n\nThe F# function to calculate the factorial of a number using recursion and handle edge cases for 0 and negative numbers is:\n\n\u0060\u0060\u0060fsharp\nlet rec factorial n =\n    if n \u003C 0 then\n        \u0022Error: Negative input\u0022\n    elif n = 0 then\n        1\n    else\n        n * factorial (n - 1)\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\nThis function will correctly calculate the factorial for non-negative integers and return an error message for negative inputs.\u0022\n     Timestamp = 2025-12-28 8:44:49 AM\n     Metadata = map [] };\n   { Id = ea14b18f-6d08-472b-9e42-68f336376114\n     CorrelationId = CorrelationId 0d682aef-f0f8-4bf5-8c99-b4b98fab0bef\n     Sender = Agent (AgentId 12b74d83-76ad-42c4-976f-6403b1e179fc)\n     Receiver = Some System\n     Performative = Inform\n     Intent = None\n     Constraints = { MaxTokens = None\n                     MaxComplexity = None\n                     Timeout = None\n                     KnowledgeBoundary = [] }\n     Ontology = None\n     Language = \u0022text\u0022\n     Content =\n      \u0022\u0060\u0060\u0060tool\n{\u0022name\u0022: \u0022write_code\u0022, \u0022arguments\u0022: {\u0022path\u0022: \u0022src/MyProject/Factorial.fs\u0022, \u0022content\u0022: \u0022let rec factorial n =\\n    if n \u003C 0 then\\n        \\\u0022Error: Negative input\\\u0022\\n    elif n = 0 then\\n        1\\n    else\\n        n * factorial (n - 1)\u0022}}\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\u0022\n     Timestamp = 2025-12-28 8:44:51 AM\n     Metadata = map [] };\n   { Id = 1b888c34-d670-4243-bcd4-3b01e4